TARGET_Blueprint: Include functions and variables that belong to this Blueprint.
TARGET_SubComponents: Include functions that belong to components of this Blueprint and/or the other target classes.
TARGET_NodeTarget: Include functions and variables that belong to the same class that the pin's node does.
TARGET_PinObject: Include functions and variables that belong to this pin type.
TARGET_SiblingPinObjects: Include functions and variables that belong to any of this node's output types.
TARGET_BlueprintLibraries: Include static functions that are globally accessible (belonging to function/macro libraries, etc.).
TARGET_NonImportedTypes: Include functions from loaded types that are not imported by this Blueprint.
ContextTargetFlagsEnd: +1 to the last flag (so we can easily iterate these flags)
